ed 3I/ATLAS, passing through our Solar System. This discovery provides a unique opportunity to study materials from other star systems. ([en.wikipedia.org](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2025_in_science?utm_source=openai))\n\n- **MethaneSAT Loses Contact:** MethaneSAT, a satellite designed to monitor global methane emissions, has lost contact and is likely not recoverable. The satellite was instrumental in tracking greenhouse gas emissions to combat climate change. ([en.wikipedia.org](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2025_in_science?utm_source=openai))\n\n**Sports:**\n\n- **Tour de France 2025 Begins:** The 112th edition of the Tour de France commenced today in Lille, France. The race spans 3,320 kilometers and will conclude on July 27 in Paris. This year's route includes seven flat stages, six hilly stages, six mountain stages, and two time trials, favoring climbers like Tadej Poga\u010dar and Jonas Vingegaard. ([cyclingnews.com](https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/tour-de-france-2025/map/?utm_source=openai))\n\n**Entertainment:**\n\n- **Oasis Announces Reunion Tour:** English rock band Oasis has reunited for the first time in 15 years, announcing their \"Oasis Live '25 Tour.\" The reunion ends years of disputes between brothers Noel and Liam Gallagher, much to the delight of fans worldwide. ([en.wikipedia.org](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2025_in_rock_music?utm_source=openai))\n\n\n## Top News Stories for July 5, 2025:\n- [Tour de France 2025 route](https://www.cyclingnews.com/races/tour-de-france-2025/map/?utm_source=openai)\n- [Nintendo Switch 2 restocks live - retailers to check now](https://www.tomsguide.com/live/news/nintendo-switch-2-restocks-news-and-updates?utm_source=openai)\n- [\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 Axios PM: Epic travel weekend](https://www.axios.com/newsletters/axios-pm-9a800950-58e6-11f0-9a9e-15eb739115ea?utm_source=openai) "
